      code: '# High availability = spread across AZs within a region\nAvailability Zones used: us-east-1a, us-east-1b, us-east-1c\n\n  Load Balancer  ── spans all 3 AZs\n  App instances  ── Auto Scaling across 1a / 1b / 1c\n  Database       ── primary in 1a, sync standby in 1b\n\n# Lose us-east-1a entirely:\n#   - LB stops routing to 1a targets\n#   - ASG launches replacements in 1b / 1c\n#   - DB fails over to the standby in 1b\n# Service stays up. Multi-region only for DR / residency.',
